ontologyFramework.OFEventManagement.OFLogicalEventManagement

Class OFEventDefinition

  • java.lang.Object
    • ontologyFramework.OFEventManagement.OFEventRepresentation
      • ontologyFramework.OFEventManagement.OFLogicalEventManagement.OFEventDefinition
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class OFEventDefinition
extends OFEventRepresentation
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class contains the initialisated definition for all the events. It collets also references to OFEventParameterDefinition. And a method to compute the event result. Which is called by OFEventAggregation.compute(OFBuildedListInvoker) and calls OFEventParameterDefinition.getParameter().
